   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🧪 LD50 Acute Toxicity Prediction — PharmaHacks 2026\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal:** Predict the log-transformed LD50 (lethal dose, 50%) of chemical compounds from their SMILES molecular structure.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pipeline Overview:**\n",
    "1. Load & explore data (TDC dataset, ~7400 molecules)\n",
    "2. Featurize molecules (Morgan fingerprints + physicochemical descriptors)\n",
    "3. Baseline model (Random Forest)\n",
    "4. Extended models (XGBoost, SVR, ensemble)\n",
    "5. Hyperparameter tuning\n",
    "6. Interpretability & error analysis\n",
    "7. Final evaluation on test set\n",
    "\n",
    "**Primary metric:** R² on held-out test set  \n",
    "**Secondary metrics:** MAE, RMSE"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "sec0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
